summary: A text message exchange from August 11, 2020, regarding coordination to contact a witness. The sender offers to provide contact information and indicates the witness has been prepped for the recipient's email.

events.title: Witness Contact Coordination
events.description: Text message exchange about reaching out to a witness, including sharing an email address and indicating the witness has been informed about the upcoming contact.

keyFacts: The document is a text message exchange dated August 11, 2020.
The subject is coordinating contact with a witness, including sharing an email address.
The witness has been informed that the recipient is 'good' and will be emailing her.
The document is marked as 'SUBJECT TO PROTECTIVE ORDER' regarding specific paragraphs.
The file references EFTA_00007565 and EFTA00158724 as identifiers.
